This directory contains email templates.
Make sure at least the following templates are defined:
- invoice
- invoice_reminder
- purchase_reminder

The structure of a skin directory must be the following:

MY_SKIN
├─ media
├─ template
│  ├─ _default (optional) -> Can contain general style elements to be included in templates
│  ├─ invoice
│  │  ├─ html.twig
│  │  ├─ subject.twig
│  │  └─ text.twig
│  ├─ invoice_reminder
│  │  ├─ html.twig
│  │  ├─ subject.twig
│  │  └─ text.twig
│  └─ purchase_reminder
│ 	  ├─ html.twig
│ 	  ├─ subject.twig
│ 	  └─ text.twig
└─ meta -> A TXT file that contains meta information about the skin
